# Keil MDK-ARM common artifacts
**/MDK-ARM/*.uvoptx
**/MDK-ARM/*.uvguix.*
**/MDK-ARM/*.bak
**/MDK-ARM/*.dep
**/MDK-ARM/*.scvd
**/MDK-ARM/*.uvgui.*
**/MDK-ARM/JLink*

# Keil MDK-ARM folders to ignore
**/MDK-ARM/Listing/
**/MDK-ARM/Output/
**/MDK-ARM/RTE/
**/MDK-ARM/DebugConfig/
**/MDK-ARM/Car_8c_PID/

# Keep source files even if in MDK-ARM (uncommon but present here)
!**/MDK-ARM/*.c
!**/MDK-ARM/*.h
!**/MDK-ARM/*.s

# STM32CubeMX
**/.mxproject
# Car_8c_PID.ioc # Usually we keep .ioc files

